1. *Užasan* mi je taj film. (I find that movie *terrible*.)
2. Taj dan je bio *užasan*. (That day was *awful*.)
3. To što si uradio je bilo *užasno*. (What you did was *horrible*.)
4. Nikada nisam čula *užasniju* priču. (I've never heard a *more terrible* story.)
5. Njegovo ponašanje je *užasno*. (His behavior is *terrible*.)
6. Osećam se *užasno* zbog onoga što sam uradio. (I feel *awful* about what I did.)
7. *Užasne* vesti su stigle iz grada. (Terrible news has arrived from the city.)
8. Sinoćnja oluja je bila *užasna*. (Last night's storm was *horrible*.)
9. *Užasni* kašalj me je držao celu noć. (I had a *terrible* cough all night.)
10. Nisam mogla da verujem koliko je *užasno* bilo gužve u gradu. (I couldn't believe how *horrible* the traffic was in the city.)